---
layout: base.njk
title: "The Japan Groove Library | The Groove Library"
description: >
  <p>Forget City Pop—we're going underground.</p>

  <p>This isn't your standard J-Pop playlist. We've curated a mix of oddball, alternative, and high-energy tracks recorded during the Olympic fever. It's a collision of eras and styles, featuring the frantic punk of Otoboke Beaver, the "Neo-Kawaii" power of CHAI, and vintage techno-pop from Plastics.</p>

  <p>Plus, we've got some rare gems, including Lene Lovich singing in Japanese.</p>

  <p>From neon-soaked synth to alleyway punk, this is the alternative sound of the city.</p>
playlist: "the-japan-groove-library"
---

{# Hero Section #}
<section class="hero hero--japan region region--lg" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center center--intrinsic flow flow--xl text-center">
      <div class="hero__eyebrow hero__eyebrow--pill text-sm text-uppercase">
        Underground sounds · Alternative vibes
      </div>

      <div class="flow flow--md">
        <h1 id="hero-heading" class="hero__title">
          The Japan Groove Library
        </h1>
        <p class="hero__tagline text-xl mx-auto">
          Neon-soaked synth to alleyway punk — the alternative sound of the city.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hero__chips cluster cluster--sm justify-center">
        <span class="hero-chip hero-chip--accent">
          <i class="fas fa-subway" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          Going underground
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


{# Description Section #}
{% if description %}
<section class="region region--lg" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="wrapper wrapper--narrow flow">
      {{ description | safe }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{# Mix Collection Section #}
<section class="region region--xl" aria-labelledby="mixes-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flow flow--xl">
      {# Section Header #}
      <div class="flow flow--sm text-center">
        <h2 id="mixes-heading" class="text-3xl">
          The Collection
        </h2>

        {% if theJapanGrooveLibrary.count > 0 %}
          <div class="cluster cluster--sm justify-center">
            <span class="badge">
              <i class="fas fa-record-vinyl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              {{ theJapanGrooveLibrary.count }} mixes in this collection
            </span>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      {# Mix Grid #}
      {% if theJapanGrooveLibrary.cloudcasts.length > 0 %}
        <div class="grid grid--2" role="list" aria-label="The Japan Groove Library mixes">
          {% for mix in theJapanGrooveLibrary.cloudcasts %}
            <div role="listitem">
              {% include "mix-player.njk" %}
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      {% elif theJapanGrooveLibrary.error %}
        {# Error State #}
        <div class="error" role="alert">
          <h3 class="error__title">
            <i class="fas fa-triangle-exclamation" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            Unable to load mixes
          </h3>
          <p>We encountered an error while fetching the music collection. Please try again later.</p>
          <details class="my-md">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-semibold">Technical details</summary>
            <p class="text-sm my-sm"><code>{{ theJapanGrooveLibrary.error }}</code></p>
          </details>
        </div>
      {% else %}
        {# Empty State #}
        <div class="center center--intrinsic flow flow--lg text-center py-3xl">
          <i class="fas fa-music-slash fa-4x text-tertiary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <div class="flow flow--sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl">No mixes available</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary">Check back soon for new content!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
